items.checkin_comment: Well, this brew has plenty of Kick for sure. Exceptionally well balanced brew that showcases clever hop alchemy. At 9.2% ABV it shows red grapefruit, dehydrated orange peel, Sauvignon Blanc must, rich burlap & spud skin velouté, dank straw & lupulin.
